{"title":"与初与终","date":"2020-02-14T17:27:07.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年2月15日","L":"2020/02/15","MM-DD":"02-15"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2020/02/15/zTNrZKV3sEQPJA5.jpg","link":"2020/02/15/与初与终","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-02-14T17:56:01.829Z","content":"<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1316479227&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<p>等风逝去<br>我们在田野里舞蹈<br>欢声笑语！<br>多么快乐的日子！  </p>\n<p>等色彩淡去<br>面容依旧<br>眼前只是一片晃白<br>无力地挣扎着坐起来  </p>\n<p>等待着等待<br>昨天、昨天还有昨天<br>还是明天、明天与明天？<br>都是一样的  </p>\n<p>风来了<br>火苗儿——<br>在我身上蔓延<br>只是温暖<br>无关与他  </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2020.02.15 午夜 </p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Promises第十一章","link":"2020/02/15/PromisesChapter11"},"next":{"title":"Promises第十章","link":"2020/02/11/PromisesChapter10"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/02/15/与初与终/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","link":"<a href=\"http://wardzhou.art/2020/02/15/与初与终/\" title=\"与初与终\">http://wardzhou.art/2020/02/15/与初与终/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}